security: Sharing this information could reveal the identities of individuals providing information to the CIA, potentially endangering their safety.
summary: A cable identifies Mr. Kanaishi Watanabe and Mr. Kenneth K. Suzuki of Trans Pacific Commerce Consultants in San Francisco.
summary_one_paragraph: This unclassified cable from an unknown sender to the Director, with copies to FE 8, DOP, CI/OPS, CI/OA, CCS 3, WW 7, and SAS 8, identifies two individuals: Mr. Kanaishi Watanabe and Mr. Kenneth K. Suzuki, who works at Trans Pacific Commerce Consultants located at Suite 315, 450 Sutter Street, San Francisco, California; the phone number is Douglas 2-6534.
title: Identification of Kanaishi Watanabe and Kenneth K. Suzuki
